Interface ActionsFunction

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    VacuumWorldActions

    public interface ActionsFunction
    Artificial Intelligence A Modern Approach (3rd Edition): page 67.

    Given a particular state s, ACTIONS(s) returns the set of actions that can be executed in s. We say that each of these actions is applicable in s.
    Author:
    Ciaran O'Reilly
